<A>__{somerset lies asleep on the bed. it is still dark outside. relatively quiet. the phone beside the inactive metronome rings harshly. somerset awakens suddenly, rankled.}
<L>__{interior mills' apartment, bedroom early morning}
<A>__{it is barely becoming light outside. mills can't sleep. alone in a double bed. he sits up, frustrated. sits on the edge of the bed and looks around. the room is a shambles, filled with moving boxes. the light coming through the window glows upon a football trophy on one box. large and noble, a golden player stands in frozen motion at the trophy's pinnacle. mills looks at the trophy and a fond smile forms on his face. the clinking of dishes and silverware is heard from another room. mills looks at the closed bedroom door, troubled.}
